        "synopsis": {
            "value": "People hear predictions on when they will die. When that time comes, a death angel appears in front of them and kills them.\n\nJung Jin-Su (Yoo Ah-In) is the head of new religion Saejinrihwe. He speaks about the \nphenomenon when death angels from Hell come and states it's a revelation from God. Jung Jin-Su has intense charisma and a mysterious aspect.\n\nBae Young-Jae (Park Jeong-Min) is a PD for a broadcasting station. He tries to dig out the truth about religious group Saejinrihwe.\n\nMin Hey-Jin (Kim Hyun-Joo) is a lawyer. She stands up against the group “Hwasalchok” (‘Arrowhead’), which consists of people who blindly follow Saejinrihwe.\n\nSong So-Hyun (Won Jin-A) is Bae Young-Jae’s wife. She collapses in emotional pain, which she can not deal with.\n\nJin Kyung-Hoon (Yang Ik-June) is a detective and investigates cases involving the appearance of angels of deaths.",
            "source": "asianwiki",
            "source_link": "https://asianwiki.com/Hellbound_(Netflix)"
        },
